cz.muni.fi.sandbox.utils.geographical
Class SjtskLocation

java.lang.Object
  cz.muni.fi.sandbox.utils.geographical.SjtskLocation

public class SjtskLocation
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing geographical location in S-JTSK coordinate system using Krovak's projection Conversion algorithm from WGS-84 (convert() method) taken over from [1]. Bibliography: 1. Hrdina, Z.; Transformace souradnic ze systemu WGS-84 do systemu S-JTSK, CVUT v Praze, Praha, 1997.
